description_no_info: Asxaan ergaa uumameera, garuu paakeejichi ammallee hin sakatta'amnee fi/ykn geejjibaan hin fudhatamne.
description_pre_transit: Geejjibaan waa'ee paakeejii odeeffannoo argateera, garuu inni hanga ammaatti sakatta'amee hin fudhanne.
description_delivery_in_progress: Paakeejiin kun naannoo naannoo ga'ee geejjibuuf adeemsa irra jira.
description_in_transit: Paakeejiin kun gara bakka itti imalutti deemaa jira. Yeroo paakeejiin gara bakka itti imalutti fooyya'iinsa gosa kanaa hedduu argachuu dandeessa.
description_customs_clearance: Paakeejiin kee gumurukaan hojjetamaa jira. Yoo barbaachise sanada dabalataa, odeeffannoo ykn kaffaltii gibiraa/gibiraaf si qunnamuu ni danda’ama. Maaloo ibsa gaafatame hatattamaan kennuudhaaf qophaa'aa.
description_return_to_sender: Paakeejichi hin geenye amma gara ergichaatti deebi'uuf karaa irra jira.
description_expired: Paakeejichi erga uumamee booda guyyoota 30f fooyya'iinsa hordoffii tokkollee hin qabu.
description_transit_limit_exceeded: Paakeejichi karaa geejjibaa keessa tureera yeroon geejjibaa idilee hayyamu caalaa dheeraa ta’a. Maaloo geejjiba qunnamaa.
description_unsuccessful_delivery: Geejjibni hin milkoofne. Yeroo baayyee tajaajilli geejjibaa ergaa dhiisee irra deebi'ee geessuuf yaala.
description_error: Sababa dhimma teeknikaatiin paaspoortii kana hordofuu hin dandeenye. Maaloo irra deebi'ii hordofaa.
description_exception: Ergaa ala ta'e kamiyyuu. Maaloo geejjiba qunnamaa.
description_available_for_pickup: Paakeejichi bakka geejjibaa irraa fudhachuuf ni danda'ama.
